# Working dropboxes — raw uploads before they get processed/placed
/Extra/
/static/models/wildlife/incoming/

# Local cold-storage for assets we've replaced/removed. Kept on disk for
# fast reference but never committed — git history holds the originals if
# they're ever needed back.
/_archive/

# Verification sandbox — playwright harness scripts (verify-*.mjs) AND the
# screenshots they produce. Everything in this folder stays local; future
# Claude sessions read it to see what's already been driven and write new
# probes/shots into it. NEVER commit anything from here.
/.verify/

# Ad-hoc perf probe — playwright-driven scene measurement, regenerated
# as needed during optimization passes.
/perf-probe.mjs

# Raw audio sources before MP3 conversion. Kept locally so the conversion
# can be re-run if MP3s need to be regenerated; never shipped.
/.audio-originals/

# Brainstorm-skill visual companion — persisted mockups + state.
/.superpowers/
# Tools — extraction scripts and compression utilities stay local; the
# blender-scripts/ folder is committed as a pattern reference for the v2
# Blender world build.
tools/bruno-analysis/
tools/compress-animations.mjs
tools/compress-glbs.mjs

# Reports — bulk Bruno extraction artifacts + working logs stay local. Only
# the two design-relevant markdowns are committed:
#   - world-design-decisions.md (brainstorm reasoning trail)
#   - v2-karan-builder-notes.md (Bruno pattern adoption guide)
reports/CHECKLIST.md
reports/blender-recreate-compare/
reports/blender-recreate-gaps.md
reports/blender-recreate-log.md
reports/bruno-*
reports/recreation-gaps.md
reports/recreation-log.md
reports/screenshots/
reports/v2-baseline-summary.md
reports/v2-coverage-report.md
reports/v2-final-index.md
reports/v2-reconstruction-test.md
